1. Selectores
Selector Universal:

* → sel-uni
Selector de Tipo:

element → sel-typ
Selector de Clase:

.class → sel-cla
Selector de ID:

#id → sel-id
Selector de Atributo:

[attribute] → sel-att

Selector de Descendiente:

ancestor descendant → sel-des
Selector de Hijo:

parent > child → sel-hij

Selector de Hermano Adyacente:

element + element → sel-her-ady

Selector de Hermano General:

element ~ element → sel-her-gen

2. Propiedades de Estilo

Color:

color → col
background-color → bac-col
border-color → bor-col

Texto:

font-family → fon-fam
font-size → fon-siz
font-weight → fon-wei
font-style → fon-sty
text-align → tex-ali
text-decoration → tex-dec
text-transform → tex-tra
line-height → lin-hei
letter-spacing → let-spa
word-spacing → wor-spa

Caja (Box Model):

width → wid
height → hei
padding → pad
border → bor
margin → mar
box-sizing → box-siz

Posicionamiento:

position → pos
top → top
right → rig
bottom → bot
left → lef
z-index → z-ind

Display:

display → dis
visibility → vis

Flexbox:

display: flex → dis-fle
flex-direction → fle-dir
flex-wrap → fle-wra
justify-content → jus-con
align-items → ali-ite
align-content → ali-con
flex-grow → fle-gro
flex-shrink → fle-shr
flex-basis → fle-bas

Grid:

display: grid → dis-gri
grid-template-columns → gri-tem-col
grid-template-rows → gri-tem-row
grid-area → gri-are
grid-column → gri-col
grid-row → gri-row
justify-items → jus-ite
align-items → ali-ite
justify-content → jus-con
align-content → ali-con

List:

list-style → lis-sty
list-style-type → lis-sty-typ
list-style-position → lis-sty-pos
list-style-image → lis-sty-im
Background:

background → bac
background-image → bac-im
background-position → bac-pos
background-size → bac-siz
background-repeat → bac-rep
Border:

border → bor
border-width → bor-wid
border-style → bor-sty
border-radius → bor-rad
border-top → bor-top
border-right → bor-rig
border-bottom → bor-bot
border-left → bor-lef
Animation:

animation → ani
animation-name → ani-nam
animation-duration → ani-dur
animation-timing-function → ani-tim-fun
animation-delay → ani-del
animation-iteration-count → ani-ite-cou
animation-direction → ani-dir
animation-fill-mode → ani-fil-mod
Transition:

transition → tra
transition-property → tra-pro
transition-duration → tra-dur
transition-timing-function → tra-tim-fun
transition-delay → tra-del

Opacity:

opacity → opa

Transform:

transform → tra
transform-origin → tra-ori
translate → tra
rotate → rot
scale → sca
skew → ske

Filter:

filter → fil
blur → blu
brightness → bri
contrast → con
drop-shadow → dro-sha
grayscale → gra
hue-rotate → hue-rot
invert → inv
opacity → opa
saturate → sat
sepia → sep

3. Unidades y Medidas
Longitud:

px → px
em → em
rem → rem
vw → vw
vh → vh
% → %
Tiempo:

s → s
ms → ms

4. Pseudo-clases y Pseudo-elementos

Pseudo-clases:

:hover → :hov
:focus → :fo
:active → :act
:visited → :vis
:link → :lin
:first-child → :fir-chil
:last-child → :las-chil
:nth-child() → :nth-chil
:nth-of-type() → :nth-typ
:not() → :not
:empty → :emp

Pseudo-elementos:

::before → ::bef
::after → ::aft
::first-line → ::fir-lin
::first-letter → ::fir-let
5. Reglas de CSS
Media Queries:
@media → @med
@import → @imp
@font-face → @fon-fac
@keyframes → @key

6. Otras Funcionalidades

Custom Properties (CSS Variables):

--variable-name → --var-nam
var(--variable-name) → var(--var-nam)
Grid Layout:

grid-template-areas → gri-tem-are
grid-template → gri-tem
grid-column-gap → gri-col-gap
grid-row-gap → gri-row-gap

Flexbox Layout:

flex-direction → fle-dir
align-self → ali-sel
align-content → ali-con
align-items → ali-ite
justify-content → jus-con